title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: Exception throws when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains highlight or map features, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export process should successfully export data from tables that contain highlight or map features without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce: 
1. Open the attached report. 
2. Export data from a table that contains highlight or map features.
